Package edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configuration

This package emulates an FPGA that can be configured with the Bitstream class and can also be read back to create bitstreams.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
BitstreamGenerator Generates a valid bitstream object from configured FPGA objects.
FPGA This class models the configuration of a Xilinx FPGA.
FPGAOperation Class for performing logical masking operations on FPGA objects.
Frame Represents a configuration frame within a Xilinx FPGA.
FrameAddressRegister Represents the contents of a Xilinx Frame Address Register and performs proper frame address register incrementing.
FrameData Defines the data contents of a configuration frame.
ReadbackFPGA Generates a configured FPGA object from a readback file.
